expandurl - extract full URL from a bit.ly URL
-----------------------------------------------

expandurl is a Perl program that converts a bit.ly shortend URL to the full
expanded URL.

Installation
------------

Copy the expandurl program to a directory of your choice.

You'll need the JSON::Any module installed, freely availible from the CPAN

Usage
-----

./expandurl http://bit.ly/a7bxX5

Configuration
-------------

You will need a bit.ly api_login and an api_key.
